    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable, showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of its class. Meticulously maintained and preserved with clinical precision, it offers an uncompromising aesthetic and mechanical profile. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a specimen of investment-grade quality for the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
