    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s a total gem. This beauty is in truly pristine, showroom-quality condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied it since day one! It drives like a dream and looks like it just rolled off the lot. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s been cared for with a lot of love and is ready for its next adventure, this is the one for you. Come take a look, you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 46500.0,
